{"tid":1766490,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［開放討論］點睇沈旭暉個‘和理非後援基金’plan","createTime":"2019-12-02T15:17:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T03:56:48.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"231f59380349ad0982d2e0a9a448fb2175e93b95","tid":1766490,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:17:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AZDnvki.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAZDnvki.png&h=1c429b91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拋磚<br />\nTLDR ：極大保留，好大陣大台味，肯定玩到歐盟咁四分五裂講唔掂數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>A. 集中啲錢整個基金，再由十長老最終決定啲錢點用</ins><br />\n<br />\n1. 大台<br />\n2. 啲錢點用，當區區議員清楚過其他人<br />\n3. 集合既錢，係咪涉及再分配？<br />\nEg有啲區會補貼其他區？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 一區之內、區與區之間，點分配政府資源已經會有衝突<br />\n依家再加多樣？<br />\n<br />\n<ins>B. 俾錢請&lsquo;社會賢達&rsquo;，&lsquo;精英&rsquo;</ins><br />\n<br />\n1. 一般情況當然唔好要人白做<br />\n不過沈生講既啲精英by definition 個個上撚哂岸啦<br />\n係有心幫既<br />\n好唔好意思喺幫義士吊命既基金攞錢出糧呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nK Kwong 何cc 大丁幾撚時出糧呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（有計劃另外籌就另一件事）<br />\n所撚謂經驗智慧<br />\n有心幫既花少少時間寫篇文<br />\n或得閒食飯過兩招，已經得啦<br />\n使唔使出糧呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請多幾個義士好過啦<br />\n<br />\n<ins>C. 十賢人+n個社區幹事 = 極官僚體系，騎劫運動</ins><br />\n1. 十賢人標準：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rrkdDnF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrrkdDnF.png&h=ac4519db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">咁既標準，你好意思一開始包埋云伯？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n沈旭暉＋鄭立共同建議：當選民主派議員捐出部分薪金支援前線義士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1751630\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1751630</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n2. 除咗練乙錚<br />\n十賢人+退休人士做既社區幹事<br />\n肯定淺黃至淺藍<br />\n本土聲音係定邊緣化<br />\n<br />\n3. 一定要重申，中國人最中意內鬥<br />\n香港社運歷史，4-5條以上政治人物長期合作冇反面收場既我真係數唔出<br />\n你同我講十個？<br />\n<br />\n4. 沈生軟實力出眾<br />\n或者西環做野<br />\n咁既體系，影響到十賢人四五個已經可以騎劫成個運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲退休高官，你估有冇野俾中共揸住<br />\n到時督灰點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小意見：<br />\n1. 錢絕不能玩中央分配<br />\n最多十八區各自夾錢<br />\n咁樣反而可以配合埋區議會選舉撥款一齊考慮<br />\nEg 有啲區政府錢俾少啲<br />\n咪基金分多啲俾佢<br />\n咁反而可以有助合作<br />\n<br />\n有乜野跨區大project，就個別考慮<br />\n<br />\n2. 啲濕鳩精英有心既非常感謝<br />\n要出糧既就算撚數啦<br />\n<br />\n3. 可以一個中央諮詢體制<br />\n幫各區解決各種申請撥款問題<br />\n但最終決策、啲錢點用一定係當區決定<br />\n甚至嚴重分歧時，最最最終區議員自己決定啲錢點用<br />\n<br />\n4. 考慮實際情況，全職議員應該比兼職議員俾少一半<br />\n人哋錢俾少咗但所有時間放落個區到"},{"pid":"2707832c5e9558894327514946e557068f0e8642","tid":1766490,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:52:12.000Z","msg":"deadline fighter 一齊寫聖誕卡畀英國歐洲議員！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1761460\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1761460</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">今晚一人一封聖誕卡</span></span><br />\n自己㨂寫畀Lords <br />\nor HKwatch的Patrons<br />\n拉落去就有哂英國議員的地址<br />\n聽日3/12 截郵，寫得一封就寄一封！<br />\n唔過10g 的空郵 $4.9郵票就夠！<br />\n仲有記得封面寫Airmail!!"},{"pid":"97bb00e3f35e2a2318c5e0c20589f798a2e752ad","tid":1766490,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:58:53.000Z","msg":"[黃色經濟圈] 時代革命由生活開始：黃色商圈已降臨（劉細良）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1766519\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1766519</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"13d6cb0a52f10be68e841cd549aed7eaf4e1f1ff","tid":1766490,"uid":74827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T03:53:50.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n沈大師抽下水屌下政府<br />\n做個學者界陶傑咪幾好<br />\n實預 就左膠味不脫嫁啦 不了"},{"pid":"892ffd22190c6bc6383e94a66e62c49cf7ac6d05","tid":1766490,"uid":74827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13d6cb0a52f10be68e841cd549aed7eaf4e1f1ff","tid":1766490,"uid":74827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T03:53:50.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n沈大師抽下水屌下政府<br />\n做個學者界陶傑咪幾好<br />\n實預 就左膠味不脫嫁啦 不了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T03:54:04.000Z","msg":"*務"},{"pid":"486cd52bbd1b5e9231626a1615d7efe0901ba937","tid":1766490,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T03:56:48.000Z","msg":"如果要長久運作<br />\n用4年打好根基<br />\n我覺得要做"}]}